{
  "texts": [
    "Ensuring ethical compliance demands transparent moral reasoning.",
    "Current black-box foundational models obscure decision logic, complicating liability assignment.",
    "Moreover, as IoA ecosystems integrate ever more heterogeneous agents, it necessites seamless interoperability on unified semantic frameworks.",
    "Future IoA systems should incorporate ethical explainability and adaptive semantic alignment.",
    "For instance, agents debate and refine value hierarchies through interaction logs and human feedback via RL [149].A key challenge is contextual ethics traceability."
  ]
}